longBusinessSummary: ImmunoPrecise Antibodies Ltd., together with its subsidiaries, engages in the antibody production and related services in the United States, Canada, Europe, and internationally. The company offers a range of antibodies, enzymes, enzyme activity assays, arthritis animal products, proteins, deiminated proteins, organoid growth factors, and hybridoma products for research purposes. Its services include custom antigen modeling, design, and manufacturing; B cell sorting, screening, and sequencing; custom, immune and naive phage display production and screening; hybridoma production with screening and clone-picking; transgenic animals and multi-species antibody discovery; antibody characterization studies, such as affinity measurements, functional assays and epitope mapping, and binning; bi-specific, tri-specific, VHH, and VNAR (shark) antibody manufacturing; DNA synthesis and cloning, protein and antibody downstream processing; antibody engineering; transient and stable cell line generation; antibody optimization and humanization; and cryopreservation. ImmunoPrecise Antibodies Ltd. was incorporated in 1983 and is based in Victoria, Canada.
